Example: Use external triggering to dynamically switch iob-in node to different states.

**Features:**
- Resend cached values (without topic change)
- Switch to new state/topic dynamically
- Check if node supports dynamic topic switching

**Usage from Function Node:**
```javascript
// Get registered nodes
const nodes = flow.get('iobroker_in_nodes') || {};
const targetNode = nodes['YOUR_NODE_ID'];

if (targetNode) {
    // Option 1: Send cached value
    targetNode.triggerCached();

    // Option 2: Switch to new topic
    if (targetNode.supportsDynamicTopic) {
        await targetNode.triggerWithTopic('system.adapter.hm-rpc.0.alive');
    }
}
```

